OL,5, People are being tricked into buying   
OL,6, homes on holiday parks where they have 
OL,7, no right to live, the BBC has found.   
OL,9,FBuyers told BBC One's Panorama they    
OL,10,Fwere cheated out of their life savings 
OL,11,Fafter being falsely promised they could
OL,12,Flive full-time on the sites.           
OL,14,FAn undercover reporter secretly filmed 
OL,15,Fone salesperson falsely claiming       
OL,16,Fyear-round living was permitted on a   
OL,17,Fholiday park in Lancashire.            
OL,19,FSite owner David Welch says contracts  
OL,20,Fclearly state it is a holiday park.    
